OL,3,CBlake Lively and Justin Baldoni settle
OL,4,C'It Ends With Us' lawsuit
OL,6,FThe high-profile legal battle between
OL,7,FBlake Lively and Justin Baldoni's
OL,8,Fproduction company will no longer go
OL,9,Fto trial after the parties announced a
OL,10,Fsettlement. Will Tullis has more
OL,12,FBlake Lively and Justin Baldoni have
OL,13,Fagreed to end their legal battle over
OL,14,Fthe acrimonious production of their
OL,15,F2024 film "It Ends With Us."
