OL,3,CBlake Lively and Justin Baldoni settle
OL,4,C'It Ends With Us' lawsuit
OL,6,FThe two sides settled their legal
OL,7,Fdispute ahead of a planned trial over
OL,8,FLively's claims that Baldoni conspired
OL,9,Fwith publicists to preemptively
OL,10,Fdestroy her reputation after she
OL,11,Fprivately accused him of sexually
OL,12,Fharassing her on the movie set.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
