OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777935793
OL,3,CBlake Lively and Justin Baldoni settle
OL,4,C'It Ends With Us' lawsuit
OL,6,FIn a joint statement, the two sides
OL,7,Fsaid: "Raising awareness, and making a
OL,8,Fmeaningful impact in the lives of
OL,9,Fdomestic violence survivors - and all
OL,10,Fsurvivors - is a goal that we stand
OL,11,Fbehind. ... It is our sincere hope
OL,12,Fthat this brings closure and allows
OL,13,Fall involved to move forward
OL,14,Fconstructively and in peace, including
OL,15,Fa respectful environment online."
OL,17,FBaldoni, who directed the film and
OL,18,Fstarred in it with Lively, had denied
OL,19,Fharassing her or orchestrating a smear
OL,20,Fcampaign.
