OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777935793
OL,3,CBlake Lively and Justin Baldoni settle
OL,4,C'It Ends With Us' lawsuit
OL,6,FHe'd claimed the complaints about his
OL,7,Fbehaviour were made up by Lively as
OL,8,Fpart of an effort to seize creative
OL,9,Fcontrol of the movie.
OL,11,FThe settlement will allow both sides
OL,12,Fto avoid a trial that would have
OL,13,Ffeatured Hollywood's ugliest side and
OL,14,Fpotentially led to more image-damaging
OL,15,Frevelations.
OL,17,FBoth actors had some of their legal
OL,18,Fclaims tossed out by the judge in
OL,19,Frecent months.
